unchilled dark side impossible.name: Unchilled Dark Side Impossible
extra: This version of the jump can be done both with and without the speed "glitch":

In the try given, Mario had an unusual amount of speed. Normally he would be capped to dive speed, but in the try given this didn't occur for unknown reasons. Because it is very easy to tell apart if Mario gained a unnormal amount of speed or not compared to a normal try, the rule that disallows this in the other version of this jump called "Chilled Dark Side Impossible" can be applied. Because the "glitch" to get this amount of speed is unknown, it makes out the biggest part in the difficulty of the jump itself.
